data.description: Welcome to this Bonaire Loft model in the beautiful Four Seasons @ South Knolls Active Adult Community. Enter to a vaulted ceiling spacious living room and dining room with a large foyer of open space as you walk through to the full eat-in kitchen and expansive peeked-ceiling Great Room. A large primary bedroom suite with double-sink full bath, and a nicely sized second bedroom all on the main floor. PLUS a large open loft that overlooks the living room, dining room, and great room complete with a third bedroom, full bath and storage room. The Spectacular Clubhouse featuring Indoor and Outdoor pools, Saunas, Billiard Rooms, Card Rooms, Fitness Center, Library, Tennis Courts, Putting Greens and MUCH MUCH MORE! Schedule a showing today!
